replies.msg:
Alex Telles said:&nbsp;&ldquo;To join a club with the prestige of Manchester United is a huge honour. You have to work hard to get to this moment in your career and now I am coming to this club, I can promise that I will give everything in my heart to be a success here.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I won many trophies at FC Porto and I want to continue that at United. The manager has a clear plan and direction for this team and I can&rsquo;t wait to pull on the famous shirt.&rdquo;

